hopobject.body: Can I take your number? protamed.com.br Yes, but due process can get ugly, and by challenging his 211-game steroid ban in connection with the Biogenesis scandal, Rodriguez could be setting himself up for the kind of scorched-earth misery that Roger Clemens, Lance Armstrong and Barry Bonds all endured amid their own doping denials. All three learned that the hidden cost of beating the rap is often seeing even more unseemly secrets make their way into the public.
